div class=\"js-gist-file-update-container js-task-list-container file-box\">\n  <div id=\"file-singleton3-java\" class=\"file my-2\">\n    \n\n  <div itemprop=\"text\" class=\"Box-body p-0 blob-wrapper data type-java  \">\n      \n<table class=\"highlight tab-size js-file-line-container\" data-tab-size=\"8\" data-paste-markdown-skip>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L1\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"1\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC1\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">public</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">class</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">Singleton3</span> {</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L2\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"2\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC2\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">/**</span></span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L3\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"3\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC3\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-c\">   * 인스턴스 사용 중 getInstance가 성능 저하가 없다면,</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L4\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"4\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC4\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-c\">   * 실행 중 수시로 체크하는 부분이 복잡하거나 성가실때,</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L5\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"5\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC5\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-c\">   * 처음부터 만들어 버린다.</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L6\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"6\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC6\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-c\">   <span class=\"pl-c\">*/</span></span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L7\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"7\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC7\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-k\">private</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">static</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">Singleton3</span> uniqueInstance <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">Singleton3</span>();</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L8\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"8\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC8\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L9\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"9\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC9\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-k\">private</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">Singleton3</span>() { }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L10\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"10\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC10\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L11\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"11\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC11\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-k\">public</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">static</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">Singleton3</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">getInstance</span>() {</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-L12\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"12\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-singleton3-java-LC12\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">    <